    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1951-08-31T19:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1951-08-31T19:00:00-05:00" n="137"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d137">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">790B.00/8–3151: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the <gloss type="to">Embassy in Burma</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">top secret</hi>
                    </seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1951-08-31T20:00:00-04:00"
                            >August 31, 1951—8 p. m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>213. Re <gloss target="#t_urtel1">urtel</gloss>s 235 Aug 29 and 245 Aug 31.<note
                        n="1" xml:id="d137fn1">See footnote 3, <ref target="#pg_291">p.
                        291</ref>.</note> Dept, after careful consideration and in light previous
                    efforts made by us with Taipei to secure removal <gloss target="#t_KMT1"
                        >KMT</gloss> troops from Burma, and bearing in mind <gloss
                        target="#t_Deptel1">Deptel</gloss> 182 Aug 22, has decided to make no
                    further efforts to restrain <gloss target="#t_GOB1">GOB</gloss> from taking
                    matter <gloss target="#t_UN1">UN</gloss>.</p>
                <p>You shld be guided accordingly in your future conversations with <gloss
                        target="#t_FonMin1">FonMin</gloss> and others.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Webb</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
